---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '../../config/site';

const title = "Legacy ESB to MuleSoft Migration";
const teaser = "Modernized a critical legacy integration layer from Informatica ESB to Anypoint Platform, reducing cycle times by 3 weeks and saving $250K annually.";
---

<BaseLayout title={`${title} | Sriman Tirupathy Eshwarappa`}>
  <article class="pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <a href="/#case-studies" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-accent text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-widest mb-12 hover:translate-x-[-4px] transition-transform">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="19" y1="12" x2="5" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 19 5 12 12 5"></polyline></svg>
        Back to Case Studies
      </a>

      <header class="mb-20">
        <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-bold text-accent mb-6">Case Study</div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 leading-tight tracking-tighter">{title}</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-outfit">{teaser}</p>
      </header>

      <div class="space-y-20">
        <!-- Styled Content Sections -->
        <div class="max-w-[900px] mx-auto pb-32">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-16">
            
            <!-- Section 1 -->
            <section>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center text-accent font-bold text-xl">1</div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tighter">Context & Objective</h2>
              </div>
              <div class="glass p-8 md:p-10">
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg mb-6">
                  The existing Informatica ESB infrastructure was reaching end-of-life and had become a bottleneck for business innovation. Cycle times were measured in months, and maintenance costs were skyrocketing.
                </p>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">
                  The objective was to migrate the mission-critical integrations to MuleSoft while ensuring zero downtime for the existing production systems.
                </p>
              </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 2 -->
            <section>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center text-accent font-bold text-xl">2</div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tighter">The Mandate</h2>
              </div>

              <div class="border-l-2 border-accent/20 pl-6 mb-10">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Key Responsibilities</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-4">
                  <li class="flex gap-3">
                    <div class="mt-1.5 text-slate-400 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"></polyline></svg></div>
                    <div class="text-slate-600 text-lg">Mapping legacy Informatica patterns to modern Mule 4 architectures.</div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex gap-3">
                    <div class="mt-1.5 text-slate-400 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"></polyline></svg></div>
                    <div class="text-slate-600 text-lg">Developing a migration factory model to accelerate payload transformations.</div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex gap-3">
                    <div class="mt-1.5 text-slate-400 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"></polyline></svg></div>
                    <div class="text-slate-600 text-lg">Implementing event-driven patterns using Solace for real-time sync.</div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex gap-3">
                    <div class="mt-1.5 text-slate-400 flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"></polyline></svg></div>
                    <div class="text-slate-600 text-lg">Validating all migrations through automated test suites and DR drills.</div>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 3 -->
            <section>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center text-accent font-bold text-xl">3</div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tighter">Measured Results</h2>
              </div>
              
              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div class="glass p-6 border-l-4 border-l-accent flex items-start gap-4">
                  <div class="mt-1 text-accent flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"></line><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"></path></svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <div class="text-slate-900 font-bold mb-1 text-xl">$250,000</div>
                    <div class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Annual savings in licensing and compute</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="glass p-6 border-l-4 border-l-accent flex items-start gap-4">
                  <div class="mt-1 text-accent flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline></svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <div class="text-slate-900 font-bold mb-1 text-xl">3 Weeks</div>
                    <div class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Saved per release cycle</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="glass p-6 border-l-4 border-l-accent flex items-start gap-4">
                  <div class="mt-1 text-accent flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"></polyline></svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <div class="text-slate-900 font-bold mb-1 text-xl">60% Reduction</div>
                    <div class="text-slate-600 text-sm">In overall technical debt</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="glass p-6 border-l-4 border-l-accent flex items-start gap-4">
                  <div class="mt-1 text-accent flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline></svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <div class="text-slate-900 font-bold mb-1 text-xl">Zero Downtime</div>
                    <div class="text-slate-600 text-sm">During production systems migration</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 4 -->
            <section>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8 mt-4">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center text-accent font-bold text-xl">4</div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tighter">Retrospective</h2>
              </div>
              
              <div class="glass p-8 md:p-10 border border-slate-200 bg-white/50 shadow-sm rounded-2xl isolate relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-accent/5 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_right,rgba(37,99,235,0.1),transparent_50%)]"></div>
                <div class="relative z-10">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-accent"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M12 16v-4"></path><path d="M12 8h.01"></path></svg>
                    If I could do it differently
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg italic">
                    "If I could do it again, I would have pushed for a 'big bang' migration on the low-complexity services rather than a purely phased approach. We spent a lot of time managing the 'dual-run' sync between Informatica and MuleSoft for simple integrations that could have been ported and switched in a single weekend with minimal risk."
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>

          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
